snippet.title: Fragile Lives of Celebrities -  Let's burn Amber ( Part 2)
snippet.description:
#JohnnyDeppsuesThe Sun for a valid reason because of their wrong portrayal of calling him a physical abuser to #AmberHeard. 

He admitted being into #Drugabuse and popping pills as a result of going through a turmoiled relationship with Amber Heard. 

Court is in favour of Johnny but this is how it all started. in this vlog I am sharing my observation on the relationship between Johnny and Winona who have a vibe of a Twinflame Couple.
Part 2 - Fragile life of Celebrities
